      World news story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Falklands finally free of landmines thanks to UK-funded team
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Demining team from Zimbabwe had to struggle with the islands’ challenging physical conditions, often working in remote locations to achieve the goal.</p>

  </div>
</div>

